    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with the ASME V&V 40 credibility factor matrix for a Class II device at MRL 2 with medium model influence. The CFD model is judged credible for its intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index predictions are supported by a validated mesh convergence study, quantitative comparison against experimental benchmark data, and appropriate model form selection. The credibility assessment supports regulatory submission.",
